Refining Pheromone Lures for the Invasive Halyomorpha halys (Hemiptera: 
Pentatomidae) Through Collaborative Trials in the United States and Europe.

Leskey TC(1)(2), Andrews H(3), Bády A(4), Benvenuto L(5), Bernardinelli I(5), 
Blaauw B(6), Bortolotti PP(7), Bosco L(8), Di Bella E(9), Hamilton G(10), Kuhar 
